Invocation Name: my silverthorne
des:
My Silverthorne by Silverthorne Homes, a Berkshire Hathaway company, is a skill to help you learn more about your new Arbor Home. This is a version of your physical homebuyers' guide for your automated home assistant. 

You can say:

"Alexa, open My Silverthorne."
"Alexa, start My Silverthorne."
"Alexa, launch My Silverthorne."

Send us an email with your suggestions at silverthorneinfo@silverthornehomes.com. Your reviews help us improve our digital services.
